Jon-Erik Hexum https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jon-Erik_Hexum 0 Jon-Erik Hexum (; November 5, 1957 – October 18, 1984) was an American actor. He died as a result of an accidental self-inflicted blank cartridge gunshot to the head on the set of the CBS television series Cover Up, in which he played the male lead.
